Attn: Estate Trustee</b>
<br/><br/>
Dear Madam/Sir: 
<br/><br/><br/>
<b>
<table style="width: 100%; ">
    <tr>
    <td style=" width:20%; vertical-align: text-bottom; padding-bottom: 10px;">Re: Bankruptcy of</td>
    <td class="second-column"> {!insolv.Debitors}
    </td>
<td>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</td>
    </tr>
    
    <tr>
